<HEADLINE>
<P>
CHINA HAILSTORM KILLS 33 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
BEIJING 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A hailstorm in the northern Chinese province of Hebei killed 33 people and 
severely injured 418 recently, the China News Service said Sunday. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Wire 
</P>
</TYPE>
