VENTURA COUNTY NEWS ROUNDUP: COUNTYWIDE; 
</P>
<P>
TRANSIT PANEL OFFERS BIKE ROUTE MAPS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By JACK SEARLES 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A free map showing Ventura County bicycle routes is being distributed by the 
county Transportation Commission. 
</P>
<P>
"Ventura County Bikeways" is available at libraries, police stations, bicycle 
shops and locations where bicycle licenses are issued, said Donna Cole, a 
commission spokeswoman. They are also available at the Ventura and Oxnard city 
halls and at commission headquarters. 
</P>
<P>
Cole said 15,000 copies of the map were printed with help from the Air 
Pollution Control District and Commuter Transportation Services, which operates 
Commuter Computer. JACK SEARLES 
</P>
