DODGER ATTENDANCE 
</P>
<P>
Sunday: 34,975 
</P>
<P>
1990 (53 dates): 1,947,448 
</P>
<P>
1989 (53 dates): 2,076,847 
</P>
<P>
Decrease: 129,399 
</P>
<P>
1990 average: 36,744 
</P>
</TEXT>
