into. "I just think there was a miscommunication," Mike Brown said regarding 
deeding of land. ; Photo, Ronald and Amy Zitka, in back yard with their 
daughter, moved Thursday into their new home on land that is subject of 
investigation. PETER ROSS / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
