</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Mitsubishi Corp. has contributed $500,000 to the University of Pittsburgh's 
Joseph Katz Graduate School of Business to establish the Mitsubishi Doctoral 
Fellowship Program in International Management. 
</P>
<P>
Mitsubishi earlier this year took a majority equity position in Aristech 
Chemical Corp. of Pittsburgh through a management-led buyout. 
</P>
<P>
Aristech Chairman Thomas Marshall in June was named the Katz School's 
Distinguished Alumnus for 1990. 
</P>
