</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Fluor Daniel Inc., Irvine, said it has been awarded a $300-million contract for 
work on a 663-megawatt power plant that will be the largest independent power 
producer in the United States when completed. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
